{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_13142.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":300701,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-1"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Hello? Is something wrong, Shizuku?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"id":300701,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-2"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"Um...I wanted to speak with you about@something."},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-3"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Does it have to do with the Union?"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story07","chara":[{"id":300701,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-4"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"Yeah... Well, you see...I'd like to join the battle."},{"chara":[{"id":300701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-5"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"You're going after Promised Blood soon, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-6"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"You weren't selected by the [textYellow:Kimochi], though..."},{"chara":[{"id":300701,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-7"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"I'm well aware."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":300701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-8"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"But I can't just sit around here and watch..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":300701,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-9"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"I don't simply want to help everyone with our@Grief Seed supply. "},{"chara":[{"id":300701,"motion":401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-10"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"I want to fight alongside you..."},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-11"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Is it because...of what happened to those@two...?"},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-12"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"To Ryo and Ikumi?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":300701,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-12"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"...[wait:1.0][chara:300701:voiceFull_fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-13][chara:300701:eyeClose_1][chara:300701:lipSynch_1]Yeah."},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-14","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-13"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Even so, I think it's best you don't get involved..."},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-15"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Even if you take your revenge, all you'll get from@it is emptiness and an unimaginably heavy burden."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":300701,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-16"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"You misunderstand."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-17"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"What...?"},{"chara":[{"id":300701,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-18"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"I can't count the number of times I've wished@we didn't have to fight like this,"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":300701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-19"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"nor can I count how often I wish the Magius@had never enacted their plans to begin with."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":300701,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-20"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"What's more, I hate Promised Blood for killing@my two friends. "},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":300701,"motion":101,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-21"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"But above all, I hate myself the most."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":300701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-22"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"I couldn't notice in time...couldn't do anything to@stop it...couldn't respond in any way but grief..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":300701,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-23"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"I'd rather help you as much as I can than@remain mired in my regrets."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100101,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-24"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Shizuku..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":300701,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-25"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"Besides, as the fight drags on, everyone loses more@and more things that are important to them."},{"chara":[{"id":300701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-26"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"I don't want to see all of our futures torn@from us..."},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"motion":301,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-27"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Shizuku..."},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-28"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"I know exactly what you mean."},{"chara":[{"id":100101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-29"},{"id":300701,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"Watching people die, watching people suffer."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":100101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-30"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"All of that erodes our hope."},{"chara":[{"id":300701,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-31"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"Exactly. I don't want to track down their killers@and kill them in turn."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":300701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-32"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"I just want to make it all stop..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100101,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-33"}],"nameLeft":"Iroha","textLeft":"The fact we have to hurt others in order to save@them is such a paradox..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":300701,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-34"}],"nameRight":"Shizuku","textRight":"Yeah..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bgm":"stop","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1,"bg":"bg_adv_21221.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":300701,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1,"turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":300701,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-35"}],"nameCenter":"Shizuku","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"black","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51042_Accomplish_feather/memoria_1279.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event05","nameNarration":"Shizuku","narration":"―Shizuku―@I'll probably become exactly@what you expected me to.","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":10,"narrationLineSpace":20,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-36"},{"narration":"―Shizuku―@I won't forgive the Magius for betraying@their allies while saying they'll save us.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-37"},{"narration":"―Shizuku―@I can't believe in the future that@those three have promised us.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-38"},{"narration":"―Shizuku―@So I'm going to put a stop to whatever it is@that the Wings of the Magius are planning.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-39"},{"nameNarration":"Ryo","narration":"―Ryo―@I won't have any regrets about letting@you go. Not even if you stop us.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-40"},{"narration":"―Ryo―@But I might cry a little, or hold a grudge.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-41"},{"narration":"―Ryo―@I'm starting to hate myself, too. I want@to save you, but I still cling to liberation.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-42"},{"nameNarration":"Ikumi","narration":"―Ikumi―@I fully intend to bring about liberation,@even if it means using the Magius.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-43"},{"narration":"―Ikumi―@I feel the same as you, Ryo.@I might cry a little, too...","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-44"},{"narration":"―Ikumi―@But, Shizuku, don't worry about us.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-45"},{"narration":"―Ikumi―@We still managed to keep from crossing a@line that no Magical Girl should cross.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-46"},{"nameNarration":"Shizuku","narration":"―Shizuku―@I knew it... You DID help me.","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-47"},{"autoTurnLast":2,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21221.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":300701,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":300701,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-48"}],"nameCenter":"Shizuku","textCenter":"The problems in the East, the dream of going on@to become an idol...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":300701,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-49"}],"nameCenter":"Shizuku","textCenter":"We were all saved, if only a little, by having our@wishes fulfilled..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":300701,"tear":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-50"}],"nameCenter":"Shizuku","textCenter":"But if we die, it all amounts to nothing."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"id":300701,"motion":0,"tear":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_102801/vo_full_102801-13-51"}],"nameCenter":"Shizuku","textCenter":"So please...let me be of use."},{"autoTurnLast":2,"bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
